data.description: SOPHISTICATED LIVING - INCREDIBLE LOCATION!!! Perfectly situated in the coveted community of Eagle Point in Aliso Viejo, this turnkey 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home offers easy living in an incredible prime location! Surrounded by delightful gardens, trees, and parks, this serene residence offers over 1,800 square feet of living space with an open floor plan, flowing with ample natural light. The expansive, remodeled kitchen with beautiful granite countertops and professional grade Thermador appliances opens to the living and dining rooms and transition through to the ground floor back patio, making for indoor-outdoor living all year long. An attached two car garage with direct access, overhead storage plus ample guest parking nearby. Close to town, nearby amazing restaurants, world famous resorts, and shopping...only minutes from your front door. The community Pool and Spa are also close by. Quick commute to John Wayne Airport, close to freeways, toll road, local beaches, wilderness trails and award-winning schools. Low tax rate and NO MELLO ROOS. LOVE WHERE YOU LIVE!
